【Description Monkey】From Amelia's secret in the
menu, you can confirm what kind of sexual
activities Amelia had.

【Description Monkey】You can switch pages using
the ←→ keys on the keyboard.

【Description Monkey】Be careful not to engage in
sexual activities in unknown places and avoid
getting into a long-lasting state.

Knowledgeable Monkey: Attributes are something
that demons and monsters inherently possess.
Depending on the compatibility of attributes,
damage can be halved or doubled.

Knowledgeable Monkey: Fire attribute demons are
weak to water. Water attribute demons are weak to
electricity. Electricity attribute demons are weak
to fire.

Knowledgeable Monkey: And dark attribute demons
are weak to light. Light attribute demons are also
weak to darkness.

Knowledgeable Monkey: It's also important to be
cautious of status ailments that each attribute
may have resistance to. If you use magic of an
attribute that is incompatible, you'll likely
struggle in battle.

Knowledgeable Monkey: You can set and use the
magic you remember in the magic selection menu.

Knowledgeable Monkey: Magic is complex and the
number of spells that can be set simultaneously is
limited. When you have more spells available, you
need to carefully consider which ones to choose.

Knowledgeable Monkey: New magic can make you
stronger in battle, or you can learn it by reading
grimoires.

【Description Monkey】There may be a mark above
your head. Light bulbs are hints or settings.
Exclamation marks are events that progress the
scenario.

【Description Monkey】The ? is a sign of the start
of a sub-event.
